-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Benchmark                   CPython zlib        zlib_py          Speedup
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
decompress   1 KB  level=1        7.1 us         1.3 us     5.66x faster
decompress   1 KB  level=6        7.0 us         2.1 us     3.34x faster
decompress   1 KB  level=9        7.0 us         2.1 us     3.33x faster
